today. actually.

121
00:04:13.086 --> 00:04:15.922
And you think that's
because he's mad at you?

122
00:04:16.006 --> 00:04:20.844
I think he feels like
I let him down. because I did.

123
00:04:20.927 --> 00:04:23.013
Jesus. with all
the martyrs around here.

124
00:04:23.096 --> 00:04:24.514
you'd think this was
a passion play.

125
00:04:24.598 --> 00:04:26.141
What's your take?

126
00:04:28.226 --> 00:04:29.561
I worked with that man
for 10 months

127
00:04:29.644 --> 00:04:30.771
while you were gone.

128
00:04:30.854 --> 00:04:32.481
He's not mad at you.

129
00:04:32.564 --> 00:04:35.650
He's mad at himself
for failing you. Rusty James.

130
00:04:35.734 --> 00:04:37.068
Really?

131
00:04:38.403 --> 00:04:40.739
Just more
White Knight/White noise.

132
00:04:40.822 --> 00:04:42.324
That's how it is.

133
00:04:44.618 --> 00:04:46.203
Share this video
with your friends if you can.

134
00:04:46.286 --> 00:04:47.537
Thank you so much.

135
00:04:47.621 --> 00:04:49.498
Be kind. be safe. be brave.

136
00:04:49.581 --> 00:04:50.624
What you doing?

137
00:04:50.707 --> 00:04:52.042
Dr. Robby. sorry.

138
00:04:52.125 --> 00:04:53.043
I was just--

139
00:04:53.126 --> 00:04:54.503
One of your TikToks? Yeah.

140
00:04:54.586 --> 00:04:56.087
About those. listen.
I'm not so sure that--

141
00:04:56.171 --> 00:04:57.923
- No. no. I was just sharing--
- No. I get it.

142
00:04:58.006 --> 00:04:59.424
I just--you know.
we do have HIPAA laws here.

143
00:04:59.508 --> 00:05:01.092
We don't let anybody film--

144
00:05:01.176 --> 00:05:02.344
I would never violate
any HIPAA laws. Dr. Robby.

145
00:05:02.427 --> 00:05:03.595
- I swear it.
- I understand.

146
00:05:03.678 --> 00:05:04.596
Even still.
we're getting behind

147
00:05:04.679 --> 00:05:05.680
