148
00:05:05.764 --> 00:05:06.681
So how about no TikTok

149
00:05:06.765 --> 00:05:09.559
on the company clock. Dr. J?

150
00:05:09.643 --> 00:05:11.478
Dr. Robby. I think you're--

151
00:05:11.561 --> 00:05:12.938
Out of touch? Probably.

152
00:05:13.021 --> 00:05:14.356
You wouldn't be the first
to accuse me of it.

153
00:05:14.439 --> 00:05:16.066
However. when I was
in medical school--

154
00:05:16.149 --> 00:05:17.943
You didn't have cell phones
or TikTok

155
00:05:18.026 --> 00:05:20.487
or internet or ICE agents
coming in here

156
00:05:20.570 --> 00:05:22.948
