and staff.

157
00:05:24.783 --> 00:05:26.284
I get it.

158
00:05:30.163 --> 00:05:33.625
We did have cell phones.
maybe not in the beginning.

159
00:05:38.338 --> 00:05:39.422
Where do you think
you're going?

160
00:05:39.506 --> 00:05:41.091
Uh. home.

161
00:05:41.174 --> 00:05:43.426
I kind of need you
to hang out a little longer

162
00:05:43.510 --> 00:05:45.345
