analog patient records.

163
00:05:45.428 --> 00:05:46.805
Normally. I would. truly.

164
00:05:46.888 --> 00:05:50.934
But I gotta get home--
wife. baby. bed.

165
00:05:51.017 --> 00:05:53.061
OK.
Go get some rest.

166
00:05:53.144 --> 00:05:54.229
You sure you're OK
to drive home?

167
00:05:54.312 --> 00:05:55.230
Absolutely.

168
00:05:55.313 --> 00:05:57.190
Just enough in the tank.

169
00:05:57.274 --> 00:05:59.276
