coming in.

177
00:06:26.469 --> 00:06:27.470
Grab the easy one.

178
00:06:27.554 --> 00:06:28.597
Bring the stabbing to Trauma 2.

179
00:06:28.680 --> 00:06:30.015
We will get the room set up.

180
00:06:30.098 --> 00:06:32.559
All right. Roger.

181
00:06:32.642 --> 00:06:36.855
OK. darling. time for this
dinosaur to head to extinction.

182
00:06:36.938 --> 00:06:38.273
Got us through
a real jam today.

183
00:06:38.356 --> 00:06:40.483
Can't thank you enough. Monica.

184
00:06:40.567 --> 00:06:41.735
Nice place to visit.

185
00:06:41.818 --> 00:06:43.153
Wouldn't want to live here
anymore.

186
00:06:43.236 --> 00:06:44.988
Oh. me. neither some days.

187
00:06:45.071 --> 00:06:46.281
But hey. Virginia Slim.

188
00:06:46.364 --> 00:06:48.283
you've come a long way.

189
00:06:48.366 --> 00:06:50.493
Glad I was wrong about you.

190
00:06:50.577 --> 00:06:51.786
Keep training 'em up right.

191
00:06:51.870 --> 00:06:53.038
I'll try.

192
00:06:53.121 --> 00:06:54.664
OK. that's enough mush.

193
00:06:54.748 --> 00:06:56.583
Back to my life
of mahjong and margaritas.

194
00:06:56.666 --> 00:06:58.001
