215
00:07:49.177 --> 00:07:50.720
So make him.

216
00:07:57.143 --> 00:07:58.103
Fuck it. Check my DMs.

217
00:07:58.186 --> 00:07:59.437
She hit me up.

218
00:07:59.521 --> 00:08:01.314
Sure. baby.
I didn't even respond.

219
00:08:01.398 --> 00:08:03.066
